  "title": "Sales Associate / Merchandiser x2 | Retail Food",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities: </p><ul><li>Ensuring that the product presentation area is clean and organized</li><li>Stocking shelves with products</li><li>Reporting complaints, problems and discrepancies to the sales manager</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Willing to travel around supermarkets (NTUC, Giant, Sheng Shiong, etc)</li><li>Have an eye for details</li><li>Creative on product presentation to improve customers engagement </li><li>Able to start short notice</li></ul><p>Other information: </p><ul><li>Basic salary $2200</li><li>Transport allowance $300</li><li>Entitled to incentive range 50-500 upon meeting target</li></ul><p><br />We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>By sending us your personal data and/or resume, you are deemed to consent to Recruit Fast Pte Ltd or its agents to collect, use and disclose your personal data and/or resume for the purpose of processing and administrating this job application.</p><p>Mandy Lim<br />Recruit Fast Pte. Ltd. (EA License: 23C1828)<br />EA Personnel: R23117478</p>",
